# ZeroExec — Complete User Walkthrough

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph LR
    Browser["🌐 Browser (React + xterm.js)"] -->|WSS + JWT| Gateway["🔒 Gateway (Go)"]
    Gateway -->|ConPTY| Agent["⚡ Agent (Windows)"]
    Gateway -->|HTTPS| Gemini["🤖 Gemini API"]
    Gateway -->|cloudflared| Cloudflare["☁️ Cloudflare Tunnel"]
    Agent -->|Job Objects| Shell["💻 PowerShell"]
```

| Component | Role |
|-----------|------|
| **Agent** | Spawns native Win32 ConPTY shells, isolated via Job Objects |
| **Gateway** | Auth (JWT), RBAC, rate limiting, audit, session recording, AI proxy |
| **Frontend** | Terminal emulator (xterm.js), Dashboard, Replay, AI Chat |

