## 🚀 Setup & Launch

### 1. Build
```powershell
.\scripts\build.ps1
```
Produces `dist/` with `zeroexec.exe`, `zeroexec-agent.exe`, `www/`, and [config.yaml](file:///c:/Users/BIT/ZeroExec/config.yaml).

### 2. Configure (Optional)
Edit [config.yaml](file:///c:/Users/BIT/ZeroExec/config.yaml):
```yaml
# AI Assistant (Feature 5)
ai:
  api_key: "YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY"   # or set VT_AI_KEY env var

# Remote Access (Feature 3)
tunnel:
  enabled: true
```

### 3. Run
```powershell
cd C:\ZeroExec
.\zeroexec.exe
```
Open **https://localhost:8081** in your browser (accept the self-signed cert).

