## End-to-End User Journey

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Browser)
    participant G as Gateway
    participant A as Agent
    participant AI as Gemini API

    U->>G: GET /auth/token
    G-->>U: JWT (role=operator)
    U->>G: WS /ws?token=...
    G->>A: StartSession (ConPTY)
    A-->>G: Session ID + PTY handle
    G-->>U: Connected ✅

    U->>G: {"type":"input","data":"ls\r"}
    G->>G: RBAC Check (allowed ✅)
    G->>A: WriteInput("ls\r")
    A-->>G: ReadOutput (file listing)
    G-->>U: {"type":"output","data":"..."}
    G->>G: Record to .vtr file

    U->>G: {"type":"input","data":"rm x\r"}
    G->>G: RBAC Check (denied 🚫)
    G->>A: WriteInput("\x03") (Ctrl+C)
    G-->>U: {"type":"error","data":"Command Blocked"}

    U->>G: POST /ai/chat (question + context)
    G->>AI: Gemini API request
    AI-->>G: Response
    G-->>U: {"reply":"..."}
```

## API Endpoints Reference

| Endpoint | Method | Auth | Description |
|----------|--------|------|-------------|
| `/ws` | WS | JWT | Terminal WebSocket |
| `/health` | GET | — | System + tunnel status |
| `/metrics` | GET | — | Session/error counters |
| `/auth/token` | GET | — | Dev token (MVP only) |
| `/admin/sessions` | GET | Admin | List active sessions |
| `/admin/terminate` | POST | Admin | Kill a session |
| `/admin/recordings` | GET | Admin | List `.vtr` recordings |
| `/admin/recording` | GET | Admin | Fetch recording file |
| `/ai/chat` | POST | JWT | AI assistant proxy |
